videos.description: Xavier Pinson loses the ball while driving to the basket, but he recovers and dishes to Jeremiah Tilmon for the dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Missouri's Tilmon jams on busted play) 2020/01/04

videos.headline: Missouri's Tilmon jams on busted play

videos.description: Kentucky's Nick Richards makes an impressive block on the defensive end, which sets up a fast break that ends with his driving layup and the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Richards' block sets up his own basket) 2020/01/04

videos.headline: Richards' block sets up his own basket

videos.description: Ashton Hagans finds Immanuel Quickley in transition, who sinks the deep three-pointer for Kentucky.

videos.headline: Quickley sinks 3 to pad Kentucky's lead
